{# Board Meeting Agenda Template
   Rendered by agenda-builder agent.
   Variables: meeting, sections, tenant_config
#}
---
**BOARD OF DIRECTORS — {{ tenant_config.company_name | upper }}**
**MEETING AGENDA**

**Meeting Type:** {{ meeting.meeting_type | title }}{% if meeting.committee_name %} — {{ meeting.committee_name }} Committee{% endif %}
**Date & Time:** {{ meeting.scheduled_at | format_datetime(tz=tenant_config.timezone, fmt="%A, %B %-d, %Y at %-I:%M %p %Z") }}
**Location:** {{ meeting.location | default("To be confirmed") }}
**Chair:** {{ meeting.chair_name | default("To be confirmed") }}

*This agenda is CONFIDENTIAL and intended solely for board members and authorized attendees.*

---

{% set ns = namespace(item_num=1) %}
{% for section in sections %}
### {{ section.section | replace("-", " ") | title }}

{% for item in section.items %}
**{{ ns.item_num }}.** {{ item.title }}{% if item.estimated_minutes %} *({{ item.estimated_minutes }} min)*{% endif %}
{% if item.presenter %}   *Presenter: {{ item.presenter }}*{% endif %}
{% if item.description %}
   {{ item.description }}
{% endif %}
{% if item.source_action_item_id %}
   *Carry-forward action item — see Prior Action Items tracker*
{% endif %}
{% set ns.item_num = ns.item_num + 1 %}
{% endfor %}

{% endfor %}

---
*Agenda prepared by the Office of the Corporate Secretary.*
*Version {{ agenda.version }} — Status: {{ agenda.status | upper }}*
*Generated: {{ now | format_datetime(fmt="%Y-%m-%d %H:%M UTC") }}*
